Class ListTag

net.minecraft.nbt.CollectionTag<net.minecraft.nbt.Tag>
net.minecraft.nbt.ListTag
public class ListTag  extends CollectionTag<Tag>
Represents a NBT Tag that can hold multiple NBT Tags in an Array.
